281
00:22:43,390 --> 00:22:45,630
Prečo si naňho nahnevaná? 

282
00:22:45,790 --> 00:22:48,000
Podľa histórie sa to naozaj stalo. 

283
00:22:58,710 --> 00:23:00,470
- Poďme. 
 - Kde? 

284
00:23:00,540 --> 00:23:03,340
No predsa do Kórey. 
